note bottom of User
  **Usage Scenarios:**

  **Before testing:**
  > STATS
  Record baseline values

  **After stress test:**
  > ERRORS
  Quick check (should be clean)

  **Troubleshooting:**
  > STATS
  Check MCB comm health,
  queue peaks, error counts

  **Performance analysis:**
  > PERF
  Throughput, uptime,
  utilization metrics
end note

@enduml
